     *
     * Crafting recipe (shapeless):
     *   4× Glass Pane + Leather + String + Enchanted Book → 1 Empty Magic Bottle
     *
     * Right-click a placed Catching Block to deposit.
     * When charged by lightning, transforms into a Charged Magic Bottle.
